{
  "chapter": "054",
  "title": "曹相国世家",
  "translations": {
    "1": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">平阳侯</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">曹参</span>，是<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">沛</span>人。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>朝时担任<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">沛</span>县的狱吏，而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">萧何</span>是主吏，两人在县里都是豪族官吏。"
    },
    "2": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高祖</span>做<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">沛</span>公起兵时，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：曹参\">参（曹参）</span>以<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">中涓</span>的身份跟随。率军<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻击</span><span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">胡</span>陵、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">方与</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">进攻</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">监公</span>的军队，大<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span>其军。向东<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻下</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">薛</span>，在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">薛</span>城西郭<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻击</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">泗水</span>郡守的军队。又<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">胡</span>陵，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">取</span>下它。改守<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">方与</span>。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">方与</span>反叛归附<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻击</span>它。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">丰</span>反叛归附<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">进攻</span>它。<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">赐爵</span>七<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大夫</span>。在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">砀</span>东<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻击</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">司马枿</span>的军队，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击破</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻下</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">砀</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">狐父</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">祁</span>的驿站。又<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">进攻</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">下邑</span>以西地区，到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">虞</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻击</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">章邯</span>的<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">车</span>骑。<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">进攻</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">爰戚</span>和<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">亢父</span>，率先登城。升迁为五<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大夫</span>。向北救援<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">阿</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻击</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">章邯</span>的军队，冲陷敌阵，追击到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">濮阳</span>。<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">进攻</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">定陶</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻取</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">临济</span>。向南救援<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">雍丘</span>。<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻击</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李由</span>的军队，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击破</span>之，<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李由</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">俘虏</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>军斥候<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">一人</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>将<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">章邯</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击破</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀死</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项梁</span>之后，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">沛</span>公与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项羽</span>率军东归。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：楚怀王\">怀王（楚怀王）</span>任命<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">沛</span>公为<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">砀</span>郡长，统领<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">砀</span>郡的军队。于是<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：曹参\">参（曹参）</span>为<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">执帛</span>，号称<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">建成君</span>。升迁为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">戚公</span>，隶属<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">砀</span>郡。"
    },
    "3": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "此后跟随<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻打</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">东郡尉</span>的军队，在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">成武</span>以南<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击破</span>之。在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">成阳</span>以南<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻击</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王离</span>的军队，又在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">杠里</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">进攻</span>它，大<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span>其军。追击败军，向西到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">开封</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻击</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">赵贲</span>的军队，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击破</span>之，把<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">赵贲</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">围</span>困在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">开封</span>城中。向西在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">曲遇</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻击</span>将军<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">杨熊</span>的军队，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击破</span>之，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">俘虏</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">司马</span>及<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">御史</span>各<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">一人</span>。升迁为<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">执珪</span>。跟随进攻<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">阳武</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻下</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">轘辕</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">缑氏</span>，阻断<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">河津</span>，回军在尸乡北<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻击</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">赵贲</span>的军队，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击破</span>之。跟随向南<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">进攻</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">犨</span>，与<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">南阳守</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：吕齮\">齮（吕齮）</span>在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">阳城</span>东郭<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">作战</span>，冲陷敌阵，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻取</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">宛</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">俘虏</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：吕齮\">齮（吕齮）</span>，完全平定<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">南阳郡</span>。又跟随向西<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">进攻</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">武关</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">峣关</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻取</span>之。前进在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">蓝田</span>以南<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">进攻</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>军，又在夜里<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻击</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>军北面，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>军大<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">败</span>，于是抵达<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">咸阳</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">灭</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>。"
    },
    "4": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项羽</span>到来，封<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">沛</span>公为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">汉王</span>。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">汉王</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：曹参\">参（曹参）</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">建成侯</span>。跟随他到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>中，升迁为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将军</span>。跟随回军平定三<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>，最先<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻打</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">下辩</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">故道</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">雍</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">斄</span>。在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">好畤</span>以南<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻击</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">章平</span>的军队，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击破</span>之，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">围</span>困<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">好畤</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻取</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">壤乡</span>。在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">壤东</span>及<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">高栎</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻击</span>三<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>的军队，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击破</span>之。再<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">围</span>攻<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">章平</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">章平</span>从<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">好畤</span>突围逃走。趁势<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻击</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">赵贲</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">内史</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：内史保\">保（内史保）</span>的军队，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击破</span>之。向东<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻取</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">咸阳</span>，改名为<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">新城</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：曹参\">参（曹参）</span>率<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">兵守</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">景陵</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">二十天</span>，三<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">章平</span>等<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻击</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：曹参\">参（曹参）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：曹参\">参（曹参）</span>出兵<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻击</span>，大<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span>其军。<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">赐食邑</span>于宁<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：曹参\">参（曹参）</span>以<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将军</span>身份领兵<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">围</span>攻<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">章邯</span>于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">废丘</span>。以<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">中尉</span>身份跟随<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">汉王</span>出<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">临晋关</span>。到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">河内</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻下</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">脩武</span>，渡过<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">围津</span>，向东在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">定陶</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻击</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">龙且</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项他</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击破</span>之。向东<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻取</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">砀</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">萧</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">彭城</span>。<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻击</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项籍</span>军，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>军大败逃走。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：曹参\">参（曹参）</span>以<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">中尉</span>身份<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">围</span>攻<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻取</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">雍丘</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王武</span>在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">黄</span>反叛，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">程处</span>在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>反叛，前往<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻击</span>，全都<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击破</span>。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">柱天侯</span>在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">衍氏</span>反叛，又进兵<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击破</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻取</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">衍氏</span>。在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">昆阳</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻击</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">羽婴</span>，追到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">叶</span>。回师<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻打</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">武彊</span>，于是到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">荥阳</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：曹参\">参（曹参）</span>从<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>中开始担任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将军</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">中尉</span>，跟随<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻打</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>，等到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项羽</span>兵败，回到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">荥阳</span>，共<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">二年</span>。"
    },
    "5": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高祖</span>某年，拜<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：曹参\">参（曹参）</span>为代理左<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>，率兵屯守<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">关中</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">一个多月</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>王<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏豹\">豹（魏豹）</span>反叛，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：曹参\">参（曹参）</span>以代理左<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>身份另与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">韩信</span>向东在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">东张</span>进攻<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>将军<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孙遫</span>的军队，大破之。趁势<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">进攻</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">安邑</span>，俘获<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>将<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王襄</span>。在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">曲阳</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻击</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>王，追到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">武垣</span>，活捉<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>王<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏豹\">豹（魏豹）</span>。<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻取</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">平阳</span>，俘获<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>王的母亲和<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">妻子</span>，完全<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">平定</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>地，共<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">五十二城</span>。<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">赐食邑</span>于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">平阳</span>。接着跟随<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">韩信</span>在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">邬</span>东<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻击</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相国</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">夏说</span>的军队，大<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span>之，<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">斩</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">夏说</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">韩信</span>与从前的<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">常山</span>王<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张耳</span>率兵攻下<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">井陉</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻击</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">成安君</span>，而<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">令</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：曹参\">参（曹参）</span>返回在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">邬</span>城中<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">围</span>困<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">别将</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：戚将军\">戚（戚将军）</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将军</span>。戚<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将军</span>突围出逃，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：曹参\">参（曹参）</span>追上去<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">斩</span>首。于是领兵到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">敖仓</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">汉王</span>所在的地方。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">韩信</span>已<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击破</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>，担任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相国</span>，向东<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻击</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：曹参\">参（曹参）</span>以右<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>的身份归属<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">韩信</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">进攻</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击破</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">历下</span>的军队，于是<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻取</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">临菑</span>。回军<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">平定</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">济北</span>郡，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">进攻</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">著</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">漯阴</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">平原</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">鬲</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">卢</span>。随后跟随<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">韩信</span>在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">上假密</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻击</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">龙且</span>的军队，大<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span>之，<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">斩</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">龙且</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">俘虏</span>他的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将军</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周兰</span>。<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">平定</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>国，共获<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">七十馀县</span>。抓获原<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>王<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田广</span>的相国<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田光</span>、他的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">守相</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">许章</span>以及从前齐国<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">胶东</span>的将军<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田既</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">韩信</span>做了<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>王，率兵到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">陈</span>，与<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">汉王</span>共同<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击破</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项羽</span>，而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：曹参\">参（曹参）</span>留下来平定<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>国还没归服的地方。"
    },
    "6": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项籍</span>死后，<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>已定，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">汉王</span>做了<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">皇帝</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">韩信</span>改封为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>王，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>改为郡。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：曹参\">参（曹参）</span>交还<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>相的<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">印</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高帝</span>任命长子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘肥\">肥（刘肥）</span>为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>王，任命<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：曹参\">参（曹参）</span>为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相国</span>。在<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高祖</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">六年</span><span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">赐爵</span>为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">列侯</span>，与<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>剖分符<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">符</span>，世世代代不绝。<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">食邑</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">平阳</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">万六百三十户</span>，号称<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">平阳侯</span>，除去以前所〖○食的采邑。"
    },
    "7": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "以<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相国</span>身份<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻击</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈豨</span>的部将<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张春</span>的军队，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击破</span>之。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">黥布</span>反叛，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：曹参\">参（曹参）</span>以<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相国</span>身份跟随<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职·规范：齐悼惠王\">悼惠王（齐悼惠王）</span>率领兵马<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">车</span>骑共<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">十二万人</span>，与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高祖</span>会合<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻击</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">黥布</span>军，大<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span>之。向南到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">蕲</span>，回军平定<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">竹邑</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">相</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">萧</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">留</span>。"
    },
    "8": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：曹参\">参（曹参）</span>的功绩：共<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻下</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二个国家，〖$一百二十二个县；俘获<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>〖$二人</span>、相<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三人</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将军</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">六人</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">大莫敖</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">郡守</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">司马</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">候</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">御史</span>各<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">一人</span>。"
    },
    "9": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "孝<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">惠帝</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">元年</span>，废除<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">诸侯相国</span>的<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">法</span>律，改任命<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：曹参\">参（曹参）</span>为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：曹参\">参（曹参）</span>做<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>相时，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>有<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">七十城</span>。<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>刚刚平定，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职·规范：齐悼惠王\">悼惠王（齐悼惠王）</span>正值青春年少，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：曹参\">参（曹参）</span>把<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">长老</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸生</span>都召集来，询问如何安抚<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">百姓</span>，但<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>原有<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸儒</span>数以百计，人人说法不同，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：曹参\">参（曹参）</span>不知该采用哪种。听说<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">胶西</span>有位<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">盖公</span>，精通<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">黄老言</span>的学说，派人带着厚礼去聘请他。见到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">盖公</span>后，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">盖公</span>向他讲述治国之道贵在<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">清静</span>而民自然安定，并由此类推详细阐述。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：曹参\">参（曹参）</span>于是让出正堂，让<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">盖公</span>居住。他治理的要领是用<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">黄老</span>之术，所以做<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>相<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">九年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>国安定，被大大称为贤相。"
    },
    "10": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">惠帝</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">二年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">萧何</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">去世</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：曹参\">参（曹参）</span>听说后，告诉<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">舍人</span>赶紧收拾行装，\"我将要入朝做相国\"。没过多久，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">使者</span>果然来召<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：曹参\">参（曹参）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：曹参\">参（曹参）</span>临行前，嘱咐他的后任相国说：\"把<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>的狱政和集市托付给你，请谨慎不要扰乱。\"后任相国说：\"治理之事没有比这更大的吗？\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：曹参\">参（曹参）</span>说：\"不是。狱政和集市，是用来容纳各种人的，如今你扰乱它，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">奸人</span>到哪里容身呢？我因此把它放在首位。\""
    },
    "11": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：曹参\">参（曹参）</span>起初身份低微时，与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">萧何</span>友好；等到都做了<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">将相</span>，有了隔阂。到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：萧何\">何（萧何）</span>临死时，推荐的贤人只有<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：曹参\">参（曹参）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：曹参\">参（曹参）</span>代替<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：萧何\">何（萧何）</span>做汉的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相国</span>，做事没有改变，完全遵循<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">萧何</span>定下的规制。"
    },
    "12": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "选择郡国中文辞朴拙、厚重老成的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">长者</span>官吏，就召来任命为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>府的属官。那些官吏言辞刻薄、追求名声的，就<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">斥</span>退他们。他日夜畅饮美酒。卿<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大夫</span>以下的官吏及<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">宾客</span>见<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：曹参\">参（曹参）</span>不理事，来的人都想劝谏几句。来的人一到，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：曹参\">参（曹参）</span>就给他们喝美酒，间或他们想要进言，又给他们喝酒，喝醉之后才离开，始终没能开口劝说，成为惯例。"
    },
    "13": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "相国府的后园靠近官吏宿舍，官吏宿舍每天饮酒唱歌呼叫。随从的官员讨厌这事，没有办法，就请<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：曹参\">参（曹参）</span>到园中游玩，他听到官吏醉酒唱歌呼喊，随从官员希望<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相国</span>召来查办他们。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：曹参\">参（曹参）</span>反而取来酒摆开座位喝酒，也跟他们一起唱歌呼应。"
    },
    "14": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：曹参\">参（曹参）</span>看到人有小过失，就一概为他掩盖，所以相国府中没什么事。"
    },
    "15": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：曹参\">参（曹参）</span>的儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：曹窋\">窋（曹窋）</span>做<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">中大夫</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">惠帝</span>怪<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相国</span>不理事，认为\"难道是瞧不起<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">朕</span>吗\"？于是对<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：曹窋\">窋（曹窋）</span>说：\"你回家后，试着私下从容问你父亲说：'<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高帝</span>刚刚离世，皇上正青春年少，您做相国，日日饮酒，不请示事务，怎么来忧虑<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>呢？'但不要说是我让你问的。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：曹窋\">窋（曹窋）</span>假沐回家，趁闲暇侍奉时，按自己所劝谏<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：曹参\">参（曹参）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：曹参\">参（曹参）</span>发怒，<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">笞</span>打<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：曹窋\">窋（曹窋）</span>二百下，说：\"赶紧入宫侍奉，<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>事不是你该说的。\"到朝见时，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">惠帝</span>责备<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：曹参\">参（曹参）</span>说：\"为什么对<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：曹窋\">窋（曹窋）</span>这么动气？上次是我让他去劝谏您的。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：曹参\">参（曹参）</span>脱帽谢罪说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>自己掂量，圣武比<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高帝</span>如何？\"皇上说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">朕</span>怎么敢比<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">先帝</span>呢！\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：曹参\">参（曹参）</span>说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>看我的才能比<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">萧何</span>谁更贤？\"皇上说：\"您似乎不及他。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：曹参\">参（曹参）</span>说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>说得对。况且<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高帝</span>与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">萧何</span>平定<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>，<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">法</span>令已经明备，如今<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>垂衣拱手，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：曹参\">参（曹参）</span>等谨守职守，遵循而不失误，不也可以吗？\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">惠帝</span>说：\"好。您休息吧！\""
    },
    "16": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：曹参\">参（曹参）</span>做汉的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相国</span>，前后共<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">三年</span>。去世后，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">谥</span>号为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：曹参\">懿侯（曹参）</span>。儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：曹窋\">窋（曹窋）</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">继承侯位。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">百姓</span>歌颂他说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">萧何</span>制定〖^法</span>令，整齐划一；<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">曹参</span>代替他，谨守而不失。推行清静之道，使百姓得以安宁统一。\""
    },
    "17": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">平阳侯</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：曹窋\">窋（曹窋）</span>，<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">高后时</span>担任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">御史大夫</span>。孝<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">文帝</span>即位，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">免</span>职为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">侯</span>。在位<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">二十九年（时长）</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">去世</span>，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">谥</span>号为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：曹窋\">静侯（曹窋）</span>。儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：曹奇\">奇（曹奇）</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名·规范：时长\">继承侯位，在位〖%七年（时长）</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">去世</span>，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">谥</span>号为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：曹奇\">简侯（曹奇）</span>。儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：曹时\">时（曹时）</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">继承侯位。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：曹时\">时（曹时）</span>娶<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平阳公主</span>，生儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：曹襄\">襄（曹襄）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：曹时\">时（曹时）</span>患癞病，归国。在位<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">二十三年（时长）</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">去世</span>，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">谥</span>号为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：曹时\">夷侯（曹时）</span>。儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：曹襄\">襄（曹襄）</span>〖=继承侯位。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：曹襄\">襄（曹襄）</span>娶<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">卫长公主</span>，生儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：曹宗\">宗（曹宗）</span>。在位<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">十六年（时长）</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">去世</span>，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">谥</span>号为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：曹襄\">共侯（曹襄）</span>。儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：曹宗\">宗（曹宗）</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">继承侯位。〖%征和</span>〖%二年</span>中，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：曹宗\">宗（曹宗）</span>因受太子之事牵连而死，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">国除</span>。"
    },
    "18": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太史公</span>说：<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">曹相国参</span>在<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>城野<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">战</span>中的功绩之所以能如此之多，是因为和<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">淮阴侯</span>一起作战。等到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩信\">信（韩信）</span>被<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">消灭</span>，而<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">列侯</span>中立功者，只有<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：曹参\">参（曹参）</span>独揽其名。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：曹参\">参（曹参）</span>担任<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相国</span>，清静的主张符合大道。而<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">百姓</span>经历<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>的残酷之后，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：曹参\">参（曹参）</span>给他们休养生息、无为而治，所以<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>都称赞他的美名。"
    },
    "19": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">曹参</span>最初起兵，是<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">沛</span>的豪族官吏。 起初跟随做<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">中涓</span>，先<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">围</span>攻驿站。 以<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">执珪</span>、执<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">帛</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>城<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">略</span>地。 <span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">衍氏</span>已被<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">昆阳</span>失守城池。 北<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">擒</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">夏说</span>，东<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">讨</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田溉</span>。 剖<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">符</span>定封，功劳无人能比。 市狱不扰，清静不事。 娶〖=平阳公主，〖=继嗣享受其利。"
    }
